                           <p xml:lang="ru">Стела в виде креста в расширяющимися концами в круге с рамкой на ступенчатом подножье.
                              Расколота на две части, сколы на рамке и на поле.</p>
                           <p xml:lang="en">Stele in the shape of a disc resting on a two-level pedestal. The front side of the disc is carved with a bas-relief of
                              a cross (with arms flaring out) encircled by a frame carved in high relief along the circumference of the disc. Split into two parts,
                           chipped along the edges of the disc and on the front surface. </p>
